```

### Available Commands

```bash
# Detect APIs in a project
mcpify detect <project_path> [--output <file>] [--openai-key <key>]

# Validate a configuration file
mcpify validate <config_file> [--verbose]

# Start an MCP server (coming soon)
mcpify start <config_file>
```

